but the the total of all the digits in a row or column is equal to 45 or box.\\\\n\\\\n7. [Can You Solve this Vampire Riddle? | NUMBER CRUSHERS](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=28cXwU-ULzk)\\\\nSource: YouTube\\xa0·\\xa0Universal Kids\\\\nCan Vicky use the five cup jar and the three cup jar to make four cups of potion or she curse to be a vampire for all time?\\\\n\\\\n8. [Only a Mastermind Can Detect the Real Vampire in This ...](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zeyQJAxzCjc)\\\\nSource: YouTube\\xa0·\\xa0MintyFifty\\\\nThink you\\'re a genius? 🤔 These BrightSide riddles will challenge your logic ... Only a Mastermind Can Detect the Real Vampire in This Puzzle 🦇.\\\\n\\\\n9. [HAPPY NEW YEAR.](https://www.facebook.com/groups/1677103935645618/posts/25825680560361285/)\\\\nSource: Facebook\\xa0·\\xa0Legacy of Kain Razielposting\\\\nThe pillars choose their guardians from birth and vampires are no longer born. This is the crux of our dilemma. And this is the terrible irony.Read more\"}',\n",
